{"title":"井架","authors":["杨佑田李连义"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":9,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"井架"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨佑田李连义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我日夜矗立在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流金泻玉的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和理想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牢固地构成九十度角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄健的歌喉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱出一首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧的乐章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不光提煤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那乌黑的晶体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还推转希望的星座"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同时把疲惫甩在井下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓缩成新的能量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的肩上扛着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信任、使命和向往"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热烈的生活"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辉煌的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管大自然对我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有严酷的时刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风摧、雨浇、霜打"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我的躯体与神经"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是中华大地给的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经得起任何磨难和损伤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我从祖国的胸膛里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不断地汲取营养"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才像今天这样身强力壮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，我把几代人的追求"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我的身架上发射出去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创造辉煌"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}